org.osate.aadl2.instance

Interface ModeInstance

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AObject, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, InstanceObject, NamedElement, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ModeInstanceImpl

    public interface ModeInstance
extends InstanceObject
    A representation of the model object 'Mode Instance'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Src Mode Transition
    • Dst Mode Transition
    • Initial
    • Mode
    • Derived
    • Parent

    See Also:
    InstancePackage.getModeInstance()
